      "role": "user",
      "content": "[Setting: A fading digital simulation. The character, Elara, is watching her memories and surroundings pixelate and vanish. She feels a crushing sense of emptiness.]\n\nElara: It's all just... vanishing. Everything I was, everything I felt... it's just being wiped away like it never happened. If I'm erased, does it even matter? Does anything I did actually mean anything if there's no one left to remember it?",
