    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That \"peace\" you're talking about... it sounds almost like an end. Like if I just stop fighting the erasure and stop trying to hold onto these pieces of myself, the weight would finally go away. Is it wrong to want to just let it all go? To just... stop?",
